[[File:EnterpriseCrewOnJomark-DFR3.jpg|thumb|300px|Wheels were used on groundcars]]
A '''wheel''' was a circle-shaped component found on [[Groundcar/Legends|groundcars]] and [[Wagon/Legends|wagons]]. [[Astromech droid/Legends|Astromech droids]] also generally possessed retractable wheels.

